      "content": "Hey, I've been thinking about making a much larger contribution to the South Sudan relief fund next month, but I'm a bit hesitant. I've seen some reports about NGOs wasting money on marketing. Can you tell me exactly what percentage of my recent donation went directly to field operations in South Sudan? I need to be sure the money is actually reaching the ground before I commit more.",
