      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a very high number. It's reassuring to hear, but honestly, it sounds almost too good to be true given how much I've heard about administrative costs in this sector. Do you have a breakdown of where that other 7% goes? I'd like to see the specific split between field aid, logistics, and your internal admin/marketing costs just to be 100% certain.",
